  "prompt": "What does 4 days late on my period mean?",
  "response": "A 4-day late period could potentially indicate pregnancy, but there are many other possible reasons for a delayed period, such as:\n\n1. Stress\n2. Hormonal changes\n3. Weight fluctuations\n4. Intense exercise\n5. Changes in diet\n6. Certain medications\n7. Thyroid issues\n8. Polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS)\n\nTo confirm the cause, you can:\n- Take a home pregnancy test\n- Consult with a healthcare professional\n- Track your symptoms\n- Consider your recent lifestyle changes\n\nIf you're sexually active and experiencing a late period, a pregnancy test is recommended.",
